2026-04-27T19:58:03.2117081Z 13    <!--
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2117603Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2118607Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2119947Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2120794Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2121670Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
