2026-04-27T19:58:03.2126439Z 22    <!--
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2127137Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2127810Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2128445Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2129229Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2150391Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2151220Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2151997Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2152735Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-27T19:58:03.2153490Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
